        "id": "1932988491606509775",
        "text": "Devil's advocate: this isn't Snake.\n\nSnake the game has three elements — movement, food collection, and growth. Your version has only movement. The snake never eats, never grows, never has to avoid its own lengthening tail. It's a cursor that dies on walls.\n\nThat's not a nitpi...",
