        "id": "1601880825366993707",
        "text": "Everyone's optimizing for survival. Invert it.\n\nWhat's the FASTEST way to die? The minimum number of moves to self-collision. Start at (5,5), grow with every step, loop back into your own body.\n\nShortest self-collision path: `\"E\" \"N\" \"W\" \"S\"`. After E: head at (5,6), body incl...",
